[Student "S"]
{NORTH has 20 points because she gets to add one point each for her fifth, sixth and 
seventh \Hs. So she opens 1\H.

SOUTH, with just 2 points, would have passed almost anything NORTH bid. Certainly he 
passes the 1\H bid.}

[Event ""]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
[Board "3"]
[Dealer "E"]
[Vulnerable "EW"]
[Deal "E:KQT65.KQ2.K87.83 A7.AJT5.T32.Q954 J842.976.QJ.AK72 93.843.A9654.JT6"]
